            <h2>Latest News<br>
            </h2>
            <dl>
              September, 2019 - X-IFU detector scientist, Sophie
              Beaumont (CRESST/UMD), begins her PhD studies in
              collaboration with IRAP in France. <br>
              November, 2019 - Athena mission successfully passed ESA
              Mission Formulation Review<br>
              January 2020 - Athena X-IFU consortium boards announced
              change of read-out baseline to time-division multiplexing
              (TDM), to be provided through the NASA contribution to
              Athena by our collaborators at NIST-Boulder.<br>
            </dl>
